      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA007.htm",
      "text": "Arise, O Jehovah, in thine anger; Lift up thyself against the rage of mine adversaries, And awake for me; thou hast commanded judgment.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
